name: Planet Bike 16g Threaded CO2 Cartridge Package
description: Threaded CO2 cartridges for Planet Bike™ Air Kiss, or Red Zeppelin CO2 Inflators. They also work with any brand of inflator that uses a threaded attachment. Each 16g canister fills a 26in. tire to 40psi, or a 700 (27in.) tire to 120psi.Contains pure CO2 with no oils or contaminants.100% recyclable steel cartridges (most MEC stores can accept these cartridges for recycling).Package of 3 or 20.
